WEBVTT

00:02.660 --> 00:06.168
You'll go to Mere. Collect my
son's bride. Take Elvina with you.

00:06.208 --> 00:08.368
- Why?
- She knows their ways.

00:08.408 --> 00:11.328
My mother wants to drive us apart.
That's why she is sending you.

00:11.368 --> 00:14.088
I've seen you look at
Elvina and her at you.

00:14.128 --> 00:15.808
It's not the way she looks at my son.

00:15.848 --> 00:17.328
- Sand wryms!
- Run!

00:20.448 --> 00:22.695
- You're alive.
- Abrecan is impatient to know if

00:22.720 --> 00:25.088
you'll help him become
Jarl of the Shieldlands.

00:25.128 --> 00:27.688
She'll not give you what you want. I can.

00:27.728 --> 00:30.448
The Warig. Their war
bands are coming together.

00:33.848 --> 00:36.168
This time, they mean to destroy us.

00:36.208 --> 00:37.608
All of us.

00:37.648 --> 00:40.288
I have a daughter to bury.

00:40.328 --> 00:42.928
You will release me, so
I can be Slean's bride.

00:43.488 --> 00:46.168
- Does your support for Rheda stand?
- It does.

