00:59.048 --> 01:02.368
Aaah!

01:19.688 --> 01:21.888
Aaah! Aaah-ah!

01:24.728 --> 01:26.728
Aaah! Aaah!

01:36.568 --> 01:38.568
Look at you now!

01:40.248 --> 01:44.048
Pig filth, scut for brains! You
should have learned to climb!

01:49.768 --> 01:52.328
Aaah! Aaah! Aaah!

02:05.888 --> 02:07.888
Fixed you, didn't I? Eh?

02:08.967 --> 02:10.967
That'll show you.

02:11.008 --> 02:13.008
You and all your kind.

